    <br /><br />

    <br />
    <img src="https://neontomo.com/img/story/beyourself.png" />
    <br /><br /><br />

    As a kid you‚Äôd find me sitting behind the TV, more fascinated by the cables instead of watching cartoons like my siblings. I still use this philosophy. Picking ideas apart, questioning rules, and making something beautiful out of what I learn.

    <br /><br />
    ![neontomo](https://neontomo.com/img/story/neonboy.jpg)

    <br /><br />
    
    **Unsurprisingly, I was a lonely kid, and when I got into adulthood I started searching for answers to the big questions.**

    In 2018 I ended up in the hospital from taking 10x the normal LSD dose, leading to a psychotic breakdown.

    ![tomo on drugs](https://neontomo.com/img/story/eye.png)

    I was falling through space, cold, alone. I felt like everyone could see how weak I was. Panic attacks daily. I fucked my future up completely.

    <br /><br /><br />
    <img src="https://neontomo.com/img/story/insane.png" />
    <br /><br /><br /><br />


    **I had a choice ahead of me.** Either I go deeper into madness and depression or I take the heavy steps towards rebuilding my life.

    I found peace while making psychedelic artworks.

    Slowly, a new identity took shape and the old Tomo died.    


    <br /><br /><div class="video-container">
    <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JTXVYYjzznM" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
    <br /><br /><br /><br />

    I found my inner power like a glowing light, leading me forward fearlessly.

    This journey started with me looking for answers to the big questions, but instead I learned that answers are overrated.

    <br /><br />
    <img src="https://neontomo.com/img/story/challenges.png" />
    <br /><br />

    I learned to keep my feet on the ground and keep asking questions.

    But no one can give me the answers.

    * If I want independence, I have to invent it.

    * If I want to work for myself, I have to build it.

    * If I want community, I have to give it.

    <br />
    Now I am an artist, because I say so.
    
    And I'm here to inspire you to be one too.
    
